WEBVTT

00:00:00.603 --> 00:00:05.555
Znam čovjeka 
koji lebdi gradom svake noći.

00:00:06.465 --> 00:00:09.459
U snovima lebdi i okreće se

00:00:09.459 --> 00:00:11.746
dok mu stopala ljube Zemlju.

00:00:12.326 --> 00:00:15.140
Sve je u pokretu, kaže on,

00:00:15.140 --> 00:00:19.002
čak i paralizirano tijelo poput njegova.

00:00:19.982 --> 00:00:23.032
On je moj otac.

00:00:24.812 --> 00:00:26.713
Prije tri godine kada sam saznala

00:00:26.713 --> 00:00:29.300
da mi je otac doživio snažan

00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:31.426
moždani udar,